<h2 id="other-considerations">Other Considerations</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Selections that use the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;=</code> or <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&gt;=</code> operators, would equate to two test cases.</li>
</ul>
